{"tid":1264343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教協呼籲同工參與七一大遊行","createTime":"2019-06-28T15:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T16:52:30.000Z","uid":198392,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d668c93c29cfe7e364a4bad8dd85c85d52d9127e","tid":1264343,"uid":198392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www2.hkptu.org/enews/2019/2019-06/0628-71march/banner-71march.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkptu.org%2Fenews%2F2019%2F2019-06%2F0628-71march%2Fbanner-71march.jpg&h=ecc3d79c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位同工：<br />\n<br />\n教協呼籲同工參與七一大遊行<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線（民陣）將於7月1日舉辦遊行，主題為：撤回惡法、林鄭下台。現時政府雖然暫緩《逃犯條例》修訂，但有關做法仍然未獲社會廣泛接受，加上政府仍然未有回應社會的其他訴求，包括成立獨立調查委員會徹底調查6月12日在金鐘的警民衝突等。因此，我們呼籲教育界結伴同行，參與由民陣發起的七一大遊行，要求政府盡快回應民間訴求。<br />\n<br />\n當天，教協理監事團隊將於下午一時半在維園草坪集合，我們邀請各位同工當天在教協旗幟下集合，加入教協的遊行隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n 【遊行詳情】<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年7月1日<br />\n路線：銅鑼灣維園草坪到金鐘政府總部<br />\n集合時間：2:30pm<br />\n集合地點：維園草坪（教協旗幟下集合）<br />\n溫馨提示：<br />\n請所有參與遊行的市民做好充足的準備，包括：水、毛巾、手機充電、雨傘、電風扇等等<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www2.hkptu.org/enews/2019/20190628-71march.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkptu.org%2Fenews%2F2019%2F20190628-71march.htm&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6vsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=e9f275f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkptu.org/enews/2019/20190628-71march.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a86a803e2e5c7753a91a28f23ccc0a46866a9638","tid":1264343,"uid":10579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e3649f1a18356108bc8bd03aa0a6eb8a4565fc","tid":1264343,"uid":10579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}